<SYNC Start=2395200><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
현장 가봤자 수사 못해.
<SYNC Start=2397020><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2397090><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
뺏어와, 당신이.
<SYNC Start=2398790><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2399010><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
나 그럴 힘 없어.
<SYNC Start=2400980><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2422580><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
어떻게 됐어요?
<SYNC Start=2424150><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2424180><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
관할서랑 연락 닿아서
<SYNC Start=2426000><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2426010><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
