<SYNC Start=2480760><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2480910><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
자문 수락하죠.
<SYNC Start=2483080><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2483230><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
OK
<SYNC Start=2484810><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2486280><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
