<SYNC Start=2489010><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2489290><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
그러시든가요.
<SYNC Start=2490740><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2491000><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
계약기간은
<SYNC Start=2492740><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2492750><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
저희쪽에서 원할 때까지.
<SYNC Start=2495270><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2495460><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
종신계약을 하자고 하시죠.
<SYNC Start=2497170><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2497190><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
그럴 수도 있고요.
<SYNC Start=2498600><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2498760><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
아, 저희가 예산이 적어서
<SYNC Start=2500960><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2500960><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
