<SYNC Start=2515210><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2515220><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
여기까지.
<SYNC Start=2516670><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2516740><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
여기까지만 하시죠, 두 분.
<SYNC Start=2518790><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2522620><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
들어가실까요?
<SYNC Start=2524310><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2536200><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
이야, 팀장님도 만만치 않네.
<SYNC Start=2540270><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2569230><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
혈흔의 방향으로 봐선.
<SYNC Start=2572010><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2572220><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
(같이)오른손잡이.
<SYNC Start=2574230><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2578390><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
그렇군요.
<SYNC Start=2580290><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2582530><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
근데
<SYNC Start=2584350><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2587410><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
