<SYNC Start=2636760><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2636760><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
다행히 현재 활력징후는<br>
안정된 상태예요.
<SYNC Start=2640070><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2640070><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
진술은 언제부터 가능할까요?
<SYNC Start=2643000><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2643770><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
