<SYNC Start=2662090><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2662090><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
어쨌든 자백을 한 용의자고, 그렇죠?
<SYNC Start=2665020><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2665020><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
