<SYNC Start=2691660><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2691750><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
아니, 참고인 조서 작성하시죠.
<SYNC Start=2695010><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2714570><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
오랜만이시네요.
<SYNC Start=2716670><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2729990><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
현재까지 밝혀진 건
<SYNC Start=2732560><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2732560><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
이정하가 박정수를 찔렀고
<SYNC Start=2735490><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2735850><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
