<SYNC Start=2742100><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2742100><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
근데 더 중요한 건
<SYNC Start=2743940><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2745230><P Class=UNKNOWNCC>
